                    As part of our team, you’ll take the lead in researching target markets and identifying potential clients. This is an excellent opportunity for someone with a keen eye for detail and who wants to grow within an international company.



Key Responsibilities:

— Conduct research to identify potential leads in target industries and markets;

— Utilize various tools and platforms to gather information on prospects.

— Qualify leads based on predefined criteria;

— Maintain and update the prospect database with accurate and detailed information;

— Provide regular reports on prospecting activities and outcomes.



Qualifications:

— Strong research skills and the ability to identify key decision-makers within organizations;

— Excellent English knowledge, both written and verbal;

— Proficient in using prospecting tools like LinkedIn Sales Navigator, Apollo, ZoomInfo, Cognism;

— Basic knowledge of Clay;

— Self-motivated and able to work independently;

— Ability to manage time effectively and meet deadlines.



Benefits: Flexible working hours to fit your schedule; Opportunity to work remotely; Competitive hourly rate; Potential for long-term opportunities.

